    "headline": "Cognex Launches Highest Performance Embedded AI Vision System Powered by Qualcomm",
    "summary": "Cognex Corporation (NASDAQ: CGNX), the global technology leader in industrial machine vision, today announced the launch of the In-Sight® 3900 Vision System. Built on a new generation of Cognex embedded AI vision technology and powered by Qualcomm Dragonwing™ platforms, the In-Sight 3900 is a fully integrated vision system that delivers industry-leading speed, accuracy, and resolution at the edge, enabling manufacturers to run demanding inspections without sacrificing throughput or simplicity.",
